figure_1.caption: Conceptual framework: The development of racial identity-rooted academic motivation at an HBCU.

claims.sentence: In Figure 1 we propose a conceptual model of how dimensions of the HBCU context cultivate African American students' academic motivation, through self-efficacy and racial identity.
